comments: Beverley (CHI) places his hand to VanVleet's (TOR) hip as he brushes the ball and marginal body contact occurs as VanVleet releases his pass attempt.
Vucevic (CHI) initiates contact with Barnes' (TOR) shoulder that affects his SQBR during the drive. The illegal contact occurs prior to the contact with the ball.
Anunoby (TOR) places his forearm to DeRozan's (CHI) front in transition and marginal contact occurs as the two come together during his drive.
Anunoby (TOR) moves along DeRozan's (CHI) path and slides his hand against DeRozan's side as he loses his footing during DeRozan's pass attempt.
Trent Jr. (TOR) contests the layup attempt and marginal body contact occurs with LaVine (CHI) after the release.
Beverley (CHI) briefly places his hand to VanVleet's (TOR) arm as the two come together underneath the basket, and they disengage from the marginal contact while pursuing the loose ball.

Replay review of the foul called on VanVleet (TOR) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed successful. VanVleet (TOR) and Beverley (CHI) get briefly tangled up during the loose ball, then VanVleet slides his hand off as the two disengage from the marginal contact.
Barnes (TOR) engages with Vucevic (CHI) off ball and marginal body contact occurs as Vucevic gathers the entry pass.
Poeltl (TOR) brings his arm toward LaVine's (CHI) path and marginal contact occurs during LaVine's drive.
Barnes (TOR) jumps alongside Caruso (CHI) and marginal body contact occurs during Caruso's upward shooting motion.
LaVine (CHI) contests VanVleet's (TOR) jump shot and the contact after the release, and follow-through, is marginal.
Vucevic (CHI) contests the layup attempt and marginal contact occurs with Barnes' (TOR) arm after the release.
Vucevic (CHI) reaches out and marginal contact occurs with Barnes' (TOR) arm during the loose ball.
Barnes (TOR) contests LaVine's (CHI) jump shot and the contact after the release, and follow-through, is marginal.
Poeltl (TOR) and Beverley (CHI) engage and disengage as marginal contact occurs during the rebound.
Beverley (CHI) initiates contact to Siakam's (TOR) front and the contact affects his SQBR during the drive.
Barnes (TOR) loses his balance and marginal body contact occurs to LaVine's (CHI) side as Barnes falls to the floor.
Barnes (TOR) lightly brushes LaVine's (CHI) arm during his drive to basket and he is able to move through the contact.
Poeltl (TOR) clamps and holds Vucevic's (CHI) arm, which affects his ability to pursue the rebound.
Anunoby (TOR) and DeRozan (CHI) come together in pursuit of the loose ball and marginal contact occurs during the rebound.
Caruso (CHI) establishes himself in Poeltl's (TOR) path and is firming up when contact occurs.
Anunoby (TOR) is called for the shooting foul during DeRozan's (CHI) jump shot attempt.  There is no clear and conclusive video evidence that confirms if the call on the floor is incorrect.
Williams (CHI) and Siakam (TOR) engage and disengage with one another and marginal contact occurs off-ball.
VanVleet (TOR) briefly engages and immediately disengages with Williams (CHI) as the pick is set.
LaVine (CHI) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he moves to imminently guard an opponent.
LaVine (CHI) jumps along Siakam's (TOR) path and marginal lower body contact occurs during Siakam's dunk attempt.
VanVleet (TOR) immediately slides his hand off of LaVine's (CHI) side and marginal contact occurs during the screen.
DeRozan (CHI) establishes himself in VanVleet's (TOR) path and marginal contact occurs as they disengage.
Anunoby (TOR) extends his leg into LaVine's (CHI) path during his drive and initiates contact to LaVine's lower body that affects his SQBR.
Anunoby (TOR) establishes himself in Williams's (CHI) path and is firming up as marginal contact occurs.
VanVleet (TOR) establishes a screening position and marginal contact occurs to Williams' (CHI) side as VanVleet attempts to slip the pick.
Caruso (CHI) jumps toward Siakam (TOR) as he gathers the ball and initiates contact to his body prior to the start of his upward shooting motion. A non-shooting foul should have been assessed.
Barnes (TOR) commits a take foul on Vucevic (CHI).
VanVleet (TOR) engages with Beverley (CHI) off-ball and marginal contact occurs as VanVleet releases away to retrieve the entry pass.
Beverley (CHI) is moving alongside Siakam's (TOR) path and marginal body contact occurs as they come together during Siakam's drive.
Beverley (CHI) contests the layup attempt and marginal body contact occurs with Siakam (TOR) after the release.
Vucevic (CHI) and Siakam (TOR) mutually engage and immediately disengage as marginal contact occurs during the rebound.
